#: src-ru/data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber:9
msgid "data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"PONY_GAME2\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"太空中，一个奇怪的物体从你身旁飘过，看起来像是巨大的显示器。突然，显示器亮了起来，你飞船上的某处响起了一段怀旧的旋律。你似乎曾在某处听过这首曲子……"

#: src-ru/data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber:11
msgid ""
"data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"PONY_GAME2\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "靠近一些。"

#: src-ru/data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber:15
msgid ""
"data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"PONY_GAME2\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "尽快离开这里，然后和船员们谈谈。"

#: src-ru/data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber:17
msgid ""
"data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"PONY_GAME2\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你不习惯相信太空中的任何显示器，尤其是巨大的那种。"

#: src-ru/data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber:4452
msgid ""
"data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber$//ship[@name=\"PONY_MONITOR_SHIPS_PARAM\"]/gotaway/text"
msgstr "那个奇怪的物体突然朝未知方向逃走了……"

#: src-ru/data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber:4459
msgid ""
"data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber$//ship[@name=\"PONY_MONITOR_SHIPS_PARAM\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "摧毁敌人后，你收集了所有幸存下来的东西……"

#: src-ru/data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber:4470
msgid ""
"data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber$//ship[@name=\"PONY_MONITOR_SHIPS_PARAM\"]/deadCrew/text"
msgstr "消灭敌方船员后，你收集了所有幸存下来的东西……"

#: src-ru/data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber:4483
msgid "data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"PONY_ADD_REWARD\"]/text"
msgstr "看来敌人的一件武器没有受损，你把它据为己有。"

#: src-ru/data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber:4804
msgid ""
"data/events_pony.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"EVENT_PONY_UPDATES5\"]/text"
msgstr "看来在加载更新期间，叛军舰队靠近了……"
